      • recommendationId

        public java.lang.String recommendationId

      • items

        public GravityItem[] items
        The list of items. This is populated only if the scenario specifies to do so, otherwise this is null. The items in this list only have the NameValues specified by the scenario. The list of NameValues specified by the scenario can be overridden by the GravityRecommendationContext.resultNameValues on a per request basis.
